node.text: Omg always go for Almond butter, the best 🤤😍

[#TheHedgehogAtHome] Can't get a cup of bubble tea yet? Never mind. Can get a cup of healthy acai instead!
.
Rewarded ourselves with this gi-normous Triple A (S$13.90+, 1-for-1 with @Burpple Beyond) from Thrive by @Boxgreenco and @AnAcaiAffair after our evening jog. Mine was drizzled with almond butter, while his was with honey. Love all the fresh fruits and superfoods, and the crunchy texture from the granolas.
.
Available for takeaway and delivery. Swipe ⬅️ for more pics.

@makanwarrior Hahaha we were actually wanting to have some ice cream that day. But ice cream parlours are closed during CB, so... acai cup it was! 😆
@ryansrule Glad you like it too, Ryan. Yums! ❤️❤️
Looks tempting and so healthy at the same time ...
@ag.foood Yes it's really refreshing! Especially good with a 1-for-1 offer! 😆
@jojoeatsbrunei Yes, do give it a try one day Jo! 😄
You know what, don’t think I’ve tried acai yet. Something to put on my to-do/eat/drink list 😄 Mmm that almond butter sounds good!
@pinkflorid Wish i could share this with you! ❤️❤️
I'd like to try all these✨😋👏😋👏✨
@anotherhungryhippo Yay Joey, i noticed that you had some acai today too! ❤️
@simplenourish Thank you Sampriti! Have a great week! ❤️
So yummy and i love the bayongs too 👌😍
Omg always go for Almond butter, the best 🤤😍
